text: Liu Xuan is the name of: *Gengshi Emperor (died 25 AD), personal name Liu Xuan, emperor of the Han dynasty *Liu Xuan (Three Kingdoms) (224–264), crown prince of Shu during the Three Kingdoms period *Liu Xuan (gymnast) (born 1979), Chinese gymnast, singer and actress *Xuan Liu (poker player) (born 1985), Canadian poker player
title: Liu Xuan
